thread.title_full: Image of Putin caressing a pregnant Trump appears on New York building | Washington Examiner

author: Caitlin Yilek
title: Image of Putin caressing a pregnant Trump appears on New York building
text:
An image of Russian President Vladimir Putin caressing a pregnant President Trump appeared on the side of a building in New York City on Valentine's Day.
The image was captioned "Love through hate."
#Trump #Putin image projected on #NYC building on 9th Avenue #Chelsea pic.twitter.com/Dzt2kSTL2e — Jeanine Ramirez (@RamirezJeanine) February 15, 2017 
Someone in Williamsburg is projecting a pregnant Trump, and Putin, on the side of a building pic.twitter.com/yFkZ0Q2eY4 — Andrew Katz (@katz) February 15, 2017 
It's the second high-profile work of art that has shown the two leaders getting friendly with one another.
